{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR","doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/YEOFRSDK"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/yeofr\/yeofrsdk\/beginenrollmentverification(identity:)"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Phase 2 of the two-phase enrolment contract: arm the verification"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"walk for a just-enrolled (in-memory, not yet persisted) identity.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Subsequent single-face, valid-framing recognition frames are","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"scored against its gallery; ","type":"text"},{"code":"enrollmentVerificationStatus","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" reports","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"live progress and, at ","type":"text"},{"code":"finishEnrollmentVerification()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" (or the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"~60 s budget), the walk’s FRR evidence —","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"recognizedFrames \/ framesVerified","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is the enrolment’s measured","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"live recognition rate, ","type":"text"},{"code":"centroidHitCounts","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" shows which centroids","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"carried it.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/YEOFRSDK\/beginEnrollmentVerification(identity:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@discardableResult"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"beginEnrollmentVerification"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"identity"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"FRSDKReturnCode","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR15FRSDKReturnCodeO","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FRSDKReturnCode"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The walk also PATCHES the gaps it measures: an FRR moment (the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"gallery fails the live user) feeds the rejected-positive capture"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pipeline — accumulate, vet (consistency 0.90), guard (anchor 0.70"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"walk-1 parity, cross-identity, novelty) — and the staged centroids"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"are appended to the in-memory gallery at finish, so the host’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"post-walk persist saves the patched gallery ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"centroidsAdded"},{"type":"text","text":" \/"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"galleryCount"},{"type":"text","text":" on the outcome; "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"rescuedFrames"},{"type":"text","text":" counts the frames a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"patch covered live). The measured FRR is always scored against the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"original gallery — patches never inflate it. Cancel discards the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"patches."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Hosts should run this between gallery completion and persisting"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the tracker, surface the rate to the user, and persist regardless"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the result (recommend a re-enrol on a low unpatched rate rather"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"than failing the save — reject loops strand users)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Returns "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".trackerIsNull"},{"type":"text","text":" when the identity isn’t enrolled or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"another session owns the embedding feed (also the constant return"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for engines without the verification walk, e.g. Luxand)."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"metadata":{"title":"beginEnrollmentVerification(identity:)","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"s:5YEOFR8YEOFRSDKC27beginEnrollmentVerification8identityAA15FRSDKReturnCodeOSS_tF","modules":[{"name":"YEOFR"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"beginEnrollmentVerification"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"identity"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR15FRSDKReturnCodeO","text":"FRSDKReturnCode"}]},"references":{"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/YEOFRSDK":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"YEOFRSDK"}],"url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/yeofrsdk","title":"YEOFRSDK","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/YEOFRSDK","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"YEOFR main entry point."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"YEOFRSDK"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR":{"url":"\/documentation\/yeofr","title":"YEOFR","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"On-device face recognition with fused liveness and TrueDepth anti-spoofing."}],"type":"topic"},"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/FRSDKReturnCode":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A normalised status code returned by the recognition engine for an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"operation such as detection, enrolment, or tracker loading."}],"fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"FRSDKReturnCode","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FRSDKReturnCode","title":"FRSDKReturnCode","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"FRSDKReturnCode","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/frsdkreturncode"},"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/YEOFRSDK/beginEnrollmentVerification(identity:)":{"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Phase 2 of the two-phase enrolment contract: arm the verification"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"walk for a just-enrolled (in-memory, not yet persisted) identity."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Subsequent single-face, valid-framing recognition frames are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"scored against its gallery; "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"enrollmentVerificationStatus"},{"type":"text","text":" reports"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"live progress and, at "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"finishEnrollmentVerification()"},{"type":"text","text":" (or the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"~60 s budget), the walk’s FRR evidence —"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"recognizedFrames \/ framesVerified"},{"type":"text","text":" is the enrolment’s measured"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"live recognition rate, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"centroidHitCounts"},{"type":"text","text":" shows which centroids"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"carried it."}],"url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/yeofrsdk\/beginenrollmentverification(identity:)","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/YEOFRSDK\/beginEnrollmentVerification(identity:)","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"beginEnrollmentVerification"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"identity"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR15FRSDKReturnCodeO","text":"FRSDKReturnCode"}],"title":"beginEnrollmentVerification(identity:)"}}}